\subsection{Key Functions to be Retained}

\begin{itemize}
  \item
    \naosix\ features: full-body movements, touch sensors, infrared and
    sonar sensors, voice recognition, and 360\textdegree\ vision.

  \item
    Existing \naosix\ apps such as \textit{Presentation}, \textit{Follow
    Me}, etc.

  \item
    WiFi and SSH connectivity of the \naosix\ robot.
\end{itemize}

\subsection{List of Functions to be Improved by the Project}

\begin{itemize}
  \item
    An intuitive web application to control and interact with the
    \naosix\ robot.

  \item
    Enhance voice recognition with AI models.

  \item
    Create a chatbot application powered by LLM models.

  \item
    Include fun animations, such as \textit{Star Wars} animated story.
\end{itemize}
